nodes.text: Art of Coloring: Star Wars: Keepsake Coloring Book

Art of Coloring: Star Wars: Keepsake Coloring Book is a children's activity book that was released as part of Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi. It was written and illustrated by Katie Cook and published by Disney–Lucasfilm Press on September 1, 2017.
A collection of Katie Cook's adorable artwork that spans the entire Star Wars saga, carefully adapted for a coloring experience that can be enjoyed by Jedi Masters and young Padawans alike.
